lyrics:
About:
This song is a tribute to a beautiful lyric by my Argentinian friend KennyDead — a brilliant writer and creator (check out his profile on producer.ai: https://www.producer.ai/KennyDead). Not a literal adaptation, but deeply inspired by his words. I'm grateful we finally made it happen.

Note: Original lyrics in Spanish with English translation on the side. They are formatted to appear as two columns on a desktop. If you are on a mobile, sorry, it will look weird.

====⭐Original upload: https://suno.com/s/ACFLqWJzOFpGKFym⭐====

